From 8bc80faa757832dd8b3d0676bb5c9fb4250f3c50 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: radhevrishi <radhev.232@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 26 May 2026 12:59:37 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] patch 0898: Signals 30 to 15 + always-visible Turnaround
 block
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

User feedback: 0897 added the Turnaround tier as conditional ("only
show when data uploaded"), so a user without turnaround data sees
nothing -> impression that the feature is broken. Plus they want the
Signals rail to be smaller (it dominates the page when full).

Two changes:

(1) Signals SHOWN cap 30 -> 15. Half the rail. Excess routes via the
    existing "+ N more · Open Signals page ->" link.

(2) Turnaround block now ALWAYS renders. When lensedTurnaround.length is 0,
    shows an empty-state card with:
      - Amber 3px left-border (consistent with the populated state)
      - "TURNAROUND BUY-ZONE (0)" header
      - One-line explanation of the playbook (inflection setups vs
        sustained-quality compounders, BUY-ZONE 1 + 2 shortlist)
      - "Upload a turnaround Screener CSV on the Turnarounds tab"
        prompt with link to /multibagger?tab=turnaround
      - Brief description of the 7-dimension scoring (earnings reversal,
        operational reset, balance-sheet repair, concall quality,
        sector tailwind, governance, valuation set-up)

Net: the block is visible on every home load. When user uploads a
turnaround CSV, it transforms into the populated DecisionTierBlock
showing top 5 BEST candidates ranked by totalScore.
---
 frontend/src/app/(dashboard)/page.tsx | 31 +++++++++++++++++++++++----
 1 file changed, 27 insertions(+), 4 deletions(-)

diff --git a/frontend/src/app/(dashboard)/page.tsx b/frontend/src/app/(dashboard)/page.tsx
index f3c636b..914a46b 100644
--- a/frontend/src/app/(dashboard)/page.tsx
+++ b/frontend/src/app/(dashboard)/page.tsx
@@ -2019,16 +2019,39 @@ export default function HomeDashboard() {
           </div>
         )}
 
-        {/* ═══════════════ PATCH 0897 — TURNAROUND TIER ═════════════════ */}
-        {lensedTurnaround.length > 0 && (
+        {/* ═══════════════ PATCH 0897/0898 — TURNAROUND TIER ═════════════
+            Always renders. When user has no turnaround data uploaded,
